ournament|2016 summer Olympics]] and won the [[2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship]].\n\n==Results==\n===Olympic Games===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Round\n!Position\n!width=\"15\"|{{Tooltip|Pld|Games played}}\n!width=\"15\"|{{Tooltip|W|Won}}\n!width=\"15\"|{{Tooltip|L|Lost}}\n!{{Tooltip|SW|Sets won}}\n!{{Tooltip|SL|Sets lost}}\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|Spain}} [[Volleyball at the 1992 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|1992]]||colspan=\"7\"|''Suspended''\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|United States}} [[Volleyball at the 1996 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|1996]]||colspan=\"7\" rowspan=\"3\"|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|Australia}} [[Volleyball at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|2000]]\n|-\n||{{Flagicon|Greece}} [[Volleyball at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|2004]]\n|-\n||{{Flagicon|China}} [[Volleyball at the 2008 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|2008]]||Quarterfinal||5th||6||2||4||6||13\n|-\n||{{Flagicon|UK}} [[Volleyball at the 2012 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|2012]]||Preliminary Round||11th||5||0||5||2||15\n|- style=\"background:silver;\"\n|{{Flagicon|Brazil}} '''[[Volleyball at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's tournament|2016]]'''||'''Final'''||{{silver02}}||8||5||3||19||11\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|JPN}} [[Volleyball at the 2020 Summer Olympics|2020]]||colspan=\"8\" rowspan=\"1\" | ''Qualified''\n|-\n!Total||colspan=\"2\"|Qualified: 3/7||19||7||12||27||39\n|}\n\n===World Championship===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Round\n!Position\n!width=\"15\"|{{Tooltip|Pld|Games played}}\n!width=\"15\"|{{Tooltip|W|Won}}\n!width=\"15\"|{{Tooltip|L|Lost}}\n!{{Tooltip|SW|Sets won}}\n!{{Tooltip|SL|Sets lost}}\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|Brazil}} [[1994 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship|1994]]||colspan=\"7\" rowspan=\"1\" | ''Banned from entering the qualifying tournaments''\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|Japan}} [[1998 FIVB Women's Volleyba