ean Volleyball League|2014]]||colspan=6 rowspan=5|''Did not enter''\n|-\n|{{flagicon|EU}} [[2015 Women's European Volleyball League|2015]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|EU}} [[2016 Women's European Volleyball League|2016]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|EU}} [[2017 Women's European Volleyball League|2017]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|HUN}} [[2018 Women's European Volleyball League|2018]]\n|-\n!Total||Qualified: 5/10 ||68||58||10||183||59\n|}\n\n==Team==\n===Current squad===\nThe following is the Serbian roster in the 2018 World Championship.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://japan2018.fivb.com/en/competition/teams/srb-serbia|title=Serbia Team Roster|date=29 September 2018 |publisher=FIVB |accessdate=29 September 2018}}</ref>\n\nHead coach: [[Zoran Terzi\u0107]]\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:100%; text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!No.\n!style=\"width:14em\"|Name\n!style=\"width:8em\"|Date of birth\n!style=\"width:9em\"|Height\n!style=\"width:9em\"|Weight\n!style=\"width:9em\"|Spike\n!style=\"width:9em\"|Block\n!Position\n!style=\"width:17em\"|2017\u201318 club\n|-\n| {{sort|01|1}} ||align=left|{{sortname|Bianka|Bu\u0161a}}||align=right|{{dts|format=dmy|1994|7|25}}||{{convert|1.87|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}}||{{convert|74|kg|lb|abbr=on}}||{{convert|312|cm|in|abbr=on}}||{{convert|298|cm|in|abbr=on}}\n|Outside Hitter|| align=\"left\" |{{flagicon|POL}} [[KPS Chemik Police|Chemik Police]]\n|-\n| {{sort|04|4}} ||align=left|{{sortname|Bojana|\u017divkovi\u0107}} ||align=right|{{dts|format=dmy|1988|3|29}}||{{convert|1.86|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}}||{{convert|70|kg|lb|abbr=on}}||{{convert|298|cm|in|abbr=on}}||{{convert|283|cm|in|abbr=on}}\n|Setter|| align=\"left\" |{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Entente sportive Le Cannet-Rocheville (volley-ball)|Le Cannet]]\n|-\n| {{sort|06|6}} ||align=left|{{sortname|Tijana|Male\u0161evi\u0107}}||align=right|{{dts|format=dmy|1991|3|18}}||{{convert|1.85|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}}||{{convert|78|kg|lb|abbr=on}}||{{convert|300|cm|in|abbr=on}}||{{convert|286|cm|in|abbr=on}}\n|Outside Hitter|| align=\"left\" |{{